ğ’ğ­ğ«ğ¢ğ§ğ : Sequence of characters (not a built-in type but provided via libraries like <string>).
ğ„ğ±ğšğ¦ğ©ğ¥ğ: string name = "John";

ğ’ğ­ğ«ğ®ğœğ­ğ®ğ«ğ: User-defined data type for grouping different types.
