ğ“ğ²ğ©ğğ¬ ğ¨ğŸ ğ•ğšğ«ğ¢ğšğ›ğ¥ğğ¬:

Local Variables: Declared inside a function or block, accessible only within that scope.

ğ†ğ¥ğ¨ğ›ğšğ¥ ğ•ğšğ«ğ¢ğšğ›ğ¥ğğ¬: Declared outside all functions, accessible to all functions in the program.

ğ‘ºğ’•ğ’‚ğ’•ğ’Šğ’„ ğ‘½ğ’‚ğ’“ğ’Šğ’‚ğ’ƒğ’ğ’†ğ’”: Retain their value between multiple function calls.

